{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_01_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 スペシャルゲストと共演",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（星見市でご当地PRイベントが開催され）\n（トークイベントにさくらが登壇することになっていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(A local promo event is being organized in Hoshimi City)\n(Sakura was to appear at a talk event)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.283257495995727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……という訳なので、ぜひみなさんも\n星見市の魅力に気付いてもらえたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And that’s why I’m really hoping all of you will\nlearn to love Hoshimi City…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そして、私達サニーピースの魅力にも！\n気付いてもらえたら嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And also learn to\nlove Sunny Peace as well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 17.764810859795773
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.815020874774817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "以上、サニーピース川咲さくらの\n星見市自慢トークでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That concludes‚ Sakura Kawasaki of Sunny Peace’s‚\nmy talk about why I’m proud of Hoshimi City!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.12831390795081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらちゃん、ありがとうございました～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much‚ Sakura!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.12831390795081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "では、次のコーナーに参りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ on to our next feature!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.928313907950816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんと、スペシャルゲストが来てくれています！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have a special guest coming to visit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.96164724128414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "星見市のマスコットキャラ『魚魚っとさん』でーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s “Gyogyoto-san”‚ Hoshimi City’s mascot character!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（登場したのは、星見市のマスコットキャラで）\n（ブサイクな見た目で有名な『魚魚っとさん』だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Out came the Hoshimi City mascot character.)\n(“Gyogyoto-san” is famous for his ugly appearance.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.64281701535701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ぎょ……魚魚っとさんだ～！\n初めて本物に出会えました～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s Gyo---Gyogyoto-san!\nI never met the real thing before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく好きなんです私！\nやったー、共演出来た！　夢みたいです！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really love him!\nYay! We’re on the same stage! It’s like a dream come true!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.444768925305304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、見て下さい\nこのぎょろっとした目……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See‚ just look at him.\nThat fishy eye…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.79476904451461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "どこ見てるか分からない感じが\nすっごく可愛いんですよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Feels like you never know where he’s looking‚\nIt’s totally cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.53762618737176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そ、そうなんですね……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you’re right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.00212523708828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "意外……ですねぇ……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… unexpected. Hahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.03545857042161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ち、ちなみに星見テレビで魚魚っとさんのアニメ化が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-actually‚ it’s been decided that Hoshimi TV will be showing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.06879190375494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "決定したそうでして、今回はそのPRに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "an anime of Gyogyoto-san‚ and for today’s promo event…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6354585704216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　アニメ化！？　ぜ、絶対観ます！\nいつ放送するんですか？　私、楽しみです！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? An anime?! That I’ve got to see!\nWhen will it be on? I can’t wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "す、凄いですね……魚魚っとさんへの愛が炸裂してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wow‚ your love for Gyogyoto-san just can’t be contained.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.50758938933501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "他にどういった所が好き……とかあるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is there anything else you like about him?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　例えば背びれの曲線美とか\nひれの色とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yes! For example‚ that curvaceous dorsal fin.\nThe color of the fins…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.13119833899133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves",
      "startTime": 104.96453167232468
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves",
      "startTime": 105.197865005658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（意外な一面を見せることが出来たのは良かったけど）\n（あまりの熱狂ぶりに時間が押してしまったな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It was a good thing to see an unexpected side of her‚)\n(but she went into such a frenzy causing time to run out…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.79786500565794,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3614.8681810746552,
          "startTime": 113.4127331867326
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves",
      "startTime": 113.4127331867326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、{user}さん！\n私、ちょっとテンション上がり過ぎちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ {user}-san!\nI guess I got a bit carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.47939985339931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves",
      "startTime": 118.77619435856158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "「締めて！」ってカンペにも全然気付かなくって……\n迷惑かけちゃいましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t notice the direction to “wrap it up!” at all…\nDid I cause a mess?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.97619435856154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんも楽しんでくれたみたいだし\n大丈夫だったと思うけど……次からは気を付けよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The audience seemed to like it‚\nso it should be fine‚ but be more careful next time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.21390526664374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves",
      "startTime": 132.81818596127994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい……そうですよね\n気を付けます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ you’re right.\nI’ll be more careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8629185091704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても意外だったな\nさくらが魚魚っとさんのファンだったなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it was quite a surprise.\nSakura being a fan of Gyogyoto-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.60410436593847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves",
      "startTime": 142.62348050422577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか？\nそんなに変なのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you think so?\nDo you find it that strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.84047614596784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなも、グッズを見せるとちょっと\n引いてる感じがあって……なんでなんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I show his merch to Sunny Peace‚ I get the feeling\nthe other girls are keeping their distance… but why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.56821745675663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves",
      "startTime": 154.3121199423017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
